snippet.title: Diablo 4 - Official Season of the Construct Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Season of the Construct, the third season of Diablo® IV, is coming January 23! Unearth a new threat looming deep beneath the sands of Kehjistan, where a tool devised for good has been overtaken for demonic evils.

#IGN #Gaming #Diablo4 #SeasonOfTheConstruct
